{"id": "1339256077665042564", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "그러면 광기 200이 되면서 30점 회복을 5번 합니다.", "timestamp": "2025-02-12T15:25:31.090000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1339256184364072970", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "회복할때마다 방패 획득 같은 창조물이랑도 엄청나게 잘 맞아요", "timestamp": "2025-02-12T15:25:56.529000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1339256227187654686", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "저게 한번에 회복되는게 아니라서, 매회복마다 방패가 생성됨", "timestamp": "2025-02-12T15:26:06.739000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
