{"id": "1339256531769757809", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "거기다가 완료불가능한 연산같은게 있다면 저 페이백 광기가 또 %로 펌핑되요", "timestamp": "2025-02-12T15:27:19.357000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
